						<p style="font-size: 4vh; color: #233A59;">Hi, my name is Aleks!</p><hr style="width:50%; border: 1px solid #233A59"><br>
						<p style="text-align:justify !important;">I am 35 years old and originally from Croatia. A large part of my family still lives in the countries of the former Yugoslavia. 
							Every time my wife Lima and I visit, we are shocked at how many dogs are sick, living on the streets, having discarded food, being hit by people and run 
							over by cars. We want to change that from the bottom of our hearts.<br><br>
							So we bought a large piece of land near Sekovici in Bosnia and are now planning the next steps to build a sanctuary for dogs in need. For this purpose we 
							founded the association "Sava Shelter e.V.". in September 2022 together with our family.<br><br>
							We hope to make the life of the Bosnian street dogs worth living in the years to come and we are very happy about any interest and help.<br><br>
							Lima & Aleks
						</p>
